videos.description: Ole Miss's Sebastian Saiz completes the and-1 play over Baylor's Johnathan Motley.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Saiz draws contact and makes the basket

videos.description: Baylor's Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. with the strong two-handed dunk and Manu Lecomte's 3-pointer help to energize the Bears' offense.
videos.headline: Baylor's offense gets spark with dunk and 3-pointer

videos.description: Ole Miss' Cullen Neal hits a deep 3-pointer and Deandre Burnett gets a steal that leads to a Sebastian Saiz jumper.
videos.headline: Ole Miss hits deep 3 and gets a steal

videos.description: Baylor's Johnathan Motley gets his own offensive rebound and draws contact as he makes the basket.
videos.headline: Motley grabs own rebound and draws and-1

videos.description: Baylor's good ball movement leads to Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. and-1 opportunity.
videos.headline: Baylor's great passing leads to and-1

videos.description: Baylor's Manu Lecomte hits a 3-pointer to cut into the Ole Miss lead.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lecomte hits corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Baylor's Manu Lecomte knocks down the 3-pointer and draws the foul to ice Ole Miss late in the second half.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lecomte completes 4-point play in win

videos.description: Baylor's Johnathan Motley talks about the comeback victory over the Ole Miss Rebels.
videos.headline: Baylor's Motley discusses comeback victory

videos.description: Miles Simon and Rich Hollenberg break down  Baylor's 3-point shooting and dominant offense against Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Baylor's 3-point shooting key to victory over Ole Miss
